</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>香港非觸式 e-道啟用 7 秒過關，加密二維碼 + 容貌識別</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/01/contactless-e-channel-to-be-launched/hottopic/spotlight/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=contactless-e-channel-to-be-launched</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 01 Dec 2021 11:20:02 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[城中熱話]]></category><category><![CDATA[過關]]></category><category><![CDATA[非觸式 e 道]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1073696</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>入境處宣佈今日正式啟用非觸式 e-道服務。合資格香港居民經香港國際機場、港珠澳大橋和深圳灣管制站出入境，可透過 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">入境處宣佈今日正式啟用非觸式 e-道服務。合資格香港居民經香港國際機場、港珠澳大橋和深圳灣管制站出入境，可透過加密二維碼配合容貌識別技術核實身分，自助辦理出入境檢查手續。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1073698" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/60FF82E2-D665-43C4-89C3-8474570F273E-694x378.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="378" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/60FF82E2-D665-43C4-89C3-8474570F273E-694x378.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/60FF82E2-D665-43C4-89C3-8474570F273E-1280x696.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/60FF82E2-D665-43C4-89C3-8474570F273E-768x418.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/60FF82E2-D665-43C4-89C3-8474570F273E-1536x836.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/60FF82E2-D665-43C4-89C3-8474570F273E-2048x1114.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/60FF82E2-D665-43C4-89C3-8474570F273E.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1073699" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/3E3D6836-5CD5-4796-ABF4-FEA884F0A712-694x387.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="387" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/3E3D6836-5CD5-4796-ABF4-FEA884F0A712-694x387.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/3E3D6836-5CD5-4796-ABF4-FEA884F0A712-1280x713.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/3E3D6836-5CD5-4796-ABF4-FEA884F0A712-768x428.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/3E3D6836-5CD5-4796-ABF4-FEA884F0A712-1536x856.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/3E3D6836-5CD5-4796-ABF4-FEA884F0A712-2048x1141.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/3E3D6836-5CD5-4796-ABF4-FEA884F0A712.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>（圖片來源：香港政府新聞網）</p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">入境處助理處長何家榮表示，非觸式 e-道的過關過程只需 7 秒 ，較之前快 1 秒。市民只要下載入境處非觸式 e-道流動應用程式，在應用程式登記後便可啟動經加密的二維碼，打開閘門進入 e-道，無須拿出身份證，亦無須使用共用指模機器。他重申系統只會比對身份證照片，不會儲存市民每次過關的相片，亦不會收集更多的個人資料，市民可以放心，亦市民並非一定要用非觸式 e-道，亦可以隨時取消登記。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1073700" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/60235C4E-440B-4975-B5B4-6B9482B6D758-694x357.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="357" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/60235C4E-440B-4975-B5B4-6B9482B6D758-694x357.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/60235C4E-440B-4975-B5B4-6B9482B6D758-1280x659.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/60235C4E-440B-4975-B5B4-6B9482B6D758-768x396.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/60235C4E-440B-4975-B5B4-6B9482B6D758-1536x791.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/60235C4E-440B-4975-B5B4-6B9482B6D758.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1073701" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/D82824F6-9E78-4416-ACB9-67AC636E6ADC-694x347.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="347" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/D82824F6-9E78-4416-ACB9-67AC636E6ADC-694x347.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/D82824F6-9E78-4416-ACB9-67AC636E6ADC-1280x640.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/D82824F6-9E78-4416-ACB9-67AC636E6ADC-768x384.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/D82824F6-9E78-4416-ACB9-67AC636E6ADC-1536x768.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/D82824F6-9E78-4416-ACB9-67AC636E6ADC-2048x1024.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/D82824F6-9E78-4416-ACB9-67AC636E6ADC.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>（圖片來源：香港政府新聞網）</p><p>何家榮指，市民在疫情下希望減少接觸共用設備，於閘內只須望向鏡頭進行容貌識別，無須共用指紋掃描器，服務也更為快捷，方便的同時也更衛生。他提到容貌識別的準成度超過 99%，且需使用的加密二維碼不能被截圖，且大約 30 秒便會刷新，在安全系數上做得很好，但部份人有機會未能用容貌識別，仍可改用手指模過關。</p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2021/11/20211130/20211130_172219_743.html">香港政府新聞網</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 :</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
